Package de.hsb.ms.syn.common.ui

Custom user interface element classes used by either the Desktop host or mobile devices.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ConnectionStatusIcon
    UI element indicator for the status of a device's connection
    DragWindow
    Custom UI element displaying a window that may be swiped in and out of the screen (Unused, incomplete implementation)
    PropertySlider
    UI element representing a slider that is linked to an algorithm's Property with additional labels depicting the function of the slider
    PropertyTable
    UI element containing multiple instances of PropertySlider for a single algorithm's Properties object.
    TouchMatrixPad
    Custom UI widget for the 2D Touch Matrix screen.
    TouchMatrixPad.TouchMatrixEvent
    Event class for TouchMatrixEvents.
    TouchMatrixPad.TouchMatrixListener
    Listener class for TouchMatrixEvents.
